# bloggen tool
generate static blogpages for a github site

## inputs
1. `/res/header.html` - html to be added to every page
1. `/res/sidecolumn.html` - a static side panel that is added to every page
1. `/posts/*` - a folder of `.txt` files with the following format:
```
Post Title
mm/dd/yy
[empty line]
post body
may be multiline
supports __markdown__
```
## outputs
1. `/blog/index.html` - archive of all posts sorted reverse chronological
1. `/blog/*.html` - each post as it's own page